These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, bus, tram
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Transport   | tram | bus | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
City: nizza, hannover, marseilles
1. the person traveling to hannover is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| City   | nizza | marseilles | hannover |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, scientific, zombie
1. the person watching scientific movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | scientific | zombie |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, prince, ritmeester
1. the prince-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Cigar   | old-henry | ritmeester | prince |

 #################################

 
