.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, scrabble
1. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Game   | snooker | scrabble | mah-jongg |

 